The '''Ministry of Defence of the [[Republic of Croatia]]''' ({{lang-hr|Ministarstvo obrane Republike Hrvatske}} or '''MORH''') is the ministry in the [[Government of Croatia]] which is in charge of the [[Republic of Croatia Armed Forces|nation's military]]. The ministry was established in 1990.

